*Njegove* knjige su veoma interesantne. (His books are very interesting.)

Njegova* obaveza je da čuva svoje stvari. (His responsibility is to look after his things.)

On je unapredio *njegove* sposobnosti. (He improved his abilities.)

Ona se oslanjala na *njegove* savete. (She relied on his advice.)

Ona je znala za *njegove* talente. (She knew about his talents.)